WEBVTT

00:03.591 --> 00:08.777
In Japan, there is an exotic female species called the Osaka obachan.

00:11.571 --> 00:15.194
You'll find them gathering in small groups, chattering away,...

00:16.521 --> 00:18.682
...always adorned in exotic plumage.

00:19.900 --> 00:21.877
They travel everywhere on bikes.

00:26.593 --> 00:29.609
They are known to be frugal and savvy shoppers,...

00:31.496 --> 00:37.966
...painstakingly inspecting merchandise and haggling down to the last yen.

00:40.470 --> 00:42.907
The unmistakable Osaka obachan.

00:44.397 --> 00:49.607
Whenever a visitor needs help, an Osaka Obachan will be ready with a treat...

00:49.972 --> 00:51.797
...and some encouraging words.

